These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, western, romance, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
House: cottage, gothic-revival, victorian, wooden
1. the victorian house is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the wooden house is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the victorian house and the person watching western movies##2
6. the gothic-revival house is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre        | romance | time-travel  | western | comedy  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| House   | victorian     | cottage | wooden       | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, juice, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, december, january
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person watching zombie movies and the person drinking sprite##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage         | cola | hot-chocolate    | sprite  | juice |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Birthday         | september | january | april | december      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, begonia, daffodil
House: colonial, modern, gothic-revival, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, house, indie
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of indie and the person who growszinnia##2
2. the colonial house is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the modern house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
5. the modern house is on the far left##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | zinnia | daffodil         | orchid   | begonia    |
| House         | modern | townhouse | colonial | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | house   | folk        | indie      | country   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, rabbit, guinea-pig
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, amber, lavender, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who likes white and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig        | chinchilla   | turtle | rabbit |
| Color         | lavender | white | amber    | yellow |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
City: new-york, berlin, venice, marseilles
House: wooden, colonial, cottage, palace
1. the palace house is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the palace house is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the wooden house is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the palace house is between the cottage house and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| City      | new-york   | berlin  | marseilles | venice     |
| House      | colonial     | palace | cottage        | wooden |

