.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, may, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, pink, lavender
1. the person who likes lavender is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who likes pink is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday          | may  | june    | november | july  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Color         | emerald | purple | lavender  | pink |

