.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, cycling, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, spy, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, engineer, firefighter, manager
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fisherman##1
2. the person watching crime movies is between the manager and the person who's sport is rowing##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the firefighter is on the right of the fisherman##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | water-polo  | rowing | cycling | skateboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | western | crime   | spy         |
| Job           | fisherman | firefighter  | engineer   | manager      |

