.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, pepper, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, chestnut, brown, blood-red
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, snooker, billiard
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who likes brown is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is between the person playing snooker and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
| Color         | blood-red | chestnut | blue  | brown |
| Game   | snooker   | billiard      | mah-jongg  | whist     |

