.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, rock, punk, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, polish, colombian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, time-travel
1. the colombian is on the far left##1
2. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
3. the fan of rock is between the fan of house and the dutch##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the polish is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the colombian##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | punk      | ambient | rock | house |
| Nationality         | colombian   | dutch  | argentine | polish |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure   | comedy | fantasy |

