.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
House: art-deco, farmhouse, wooden, townhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, cricket, water-polo
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the townhouse house##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| House    | townhouse  | wooden | art-deco | farmhouse     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Sport     | weightlifting        | water-polo       | skateboarding      | cricket |

