.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, backgammon, go
There are 4 different nationalities: american, pakistani, malaysian, canadian
4 different pets are kept: bird, goat, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the canadian is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing billiard is between the person playing backgammon and the pakistani##2
4. the malaysian is on the far left##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Game   | go | backgammon     | billiard | monopoly       |
| Nationality      | malaysian  | canadian | american  | pakistani |
| Pet        | turtle  | goat      | pony        | bird      |

