.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, daisy, begonia
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, orange, cabbage, potato
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who growsdaisy and the person eating cauliflower##2
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating orange##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia  | daisy       | poppy   |
| Food      | cauliflower     | cabbage | orange | potato |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

