.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, egyptian, german
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, pall-mall, vegafina, ritmeester
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, ship, trike
1. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the ship is the egyptian##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the indonesian##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the vegafina-smoker and the egyptian##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Nationality           | indian | german | egyptian    | indonesian   |
| Cigar   | vegafina      | pall-mall   | ritmeester | swisher |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus       | ship        | trike    |

