3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
5. the person eating banana is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating potato##1
7. the person eating potato is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating banana##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | fishing   | chess           | baking         | skydiving      |
| Movie-Genre     | satire | family | martial-arts | time-travel |
| Food   | lettuce     | banana         | potato       | broccoli        |

