The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, azalea, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsazalea is between the fan of gospel and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
6. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
7. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | ambient | gospel           | indie |
| Flower       | amaryllis | azalea    | aconite          | zinnia   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

