3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating raspberry is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person eating kiwi and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
