.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, november, august
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, apricot, green, azure
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes azure is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who likes green##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | august | january | march | november |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Color   | white | apricot | green | azure |

 